post_summaries.description: The image shows a person in a wheelchair on a wooden platform in a forest setting. They are wearing a red helmet and laughing, with another person in a blue shirt and a third person helping to guide the wheelchair. The post includes the hashtags #supportworker and #accessibilityforall.

The image is a digital drawing of Gisele Pelicot, with a speech bubble containing the Spanish phrase "Que la verg√ºenza cambie de lado" (May shame change sides). The drawing is signed "Sofia Weidner".

The image shows a person sitting in a car, presumably as a passenger, with their feet up on the dashboard. The background shows a clear blue sky and trees, suggesting they are on a road trip. The location tag indicates they are on the Hume Highway in New South Wales, Australia.

The image shows a spread of snacks and drinks, including chips, dips, ginger beer, and what appears to be pickled items. A TV is on in the background, displaying an animated show. The hashtags in the caption indicate the show is by zerocalcare.

The image shows a variety of spices and seasonings, including truffle salt, garlic salt, smoked paprika, Mexican seasoning, chili flakes, "Vacon" (likely vegan bacon seasoning), and Bull's-Eye BBQ sauce. The post is tagged with #vegan, #inspiration, #sazon, #dinnerideas, and #seasonings.

The Instagram post by _organic_cookie features a video of an Iranian rock climbing athlete who competed in South Korea. The video also references the protests against the Iranian regime and the #MahsaAmini movement.
